column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "ED257E2C48DB6620139C4B954C7B5F2C", "Who are you? I won\'t let anyone mess up this place!")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "9996C47D46724D2C2E32908365AA5651", "Don\'t worry. We\'re just travelling through to save the island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "425180614284146C467CF4BDD6F9FFE5", "I don\'t trust you, get lost!")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "ED1D52D54494644A50DE3AA3489B16CC", "Wait a sec.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "7B3D5A3345430807FD4BBBABBE2F230A", "Are you by any chance...?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "EAC2F5244588D726CE8CC3BDCD6254E5", "I told you so!")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "984F47AB471B91DA75CF08992E41B1FE", "I\'m sorry. We don\'t get visitors often, so I get excited about my new job.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "A6B3A4E841A0F3DB7C5D99A5F1C45234", "I\'m guarding a place called Ancient Dino Region.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "F8F6778F4115097355F530A82E16D4D9", "It\'s an unexplored region.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "C7E718614B4B66AF51C4F38F7FB63E01", "Will you show me around?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "E7F8E5F948F02DF814658EB0D6BA70E6", "Ancient Dino Region is divided in two sections.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "72C549C045B88B90C814F48F6E020892", "Where we live is called Glacial Time Zone.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "9942C9B94A5A76224EBD86A9F3A114B4", "It\'s a special place where time goes slow.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "D161D7A24FE7B9F04F21A9B1DD2D2DFF", "Time goes slow?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "EFAC872E414508F43F565F8804BE7F73", "The other place is Speedy Time Zone.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "65650EF3412DD94979EF4DBC2E11204B", "It\'s dangerous and further than the Glacial Time Zone.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "1F3C010144F13629C8216294A3B98BF2", "It\'s dangerous cuz time goes very fast.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "288677834CB5E73A99B2B08DE0654A45", "The land is bare. Bones and fossils everywhere.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "FE715570459FACE7C1FE13BA9B482CB7", "That\'s cuz time passes faster there than in other places?")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "D1B55E60442DF0F7342EDCBC1B9B49F7", "Right. Don\'t stay there long.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "D3CE781A43E08A50B3916AA5ACAC2017", "Since I\'m blocking your way, you can\'t go there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "6B35BB364FAD13E3775E6B93E779261C", "I was unlucky! It doesn\'t happen often.")
NSLOCTEXT("[C91D465D4A7637FE58C17D8D11111242]", "498DAD454E9D8C06EB87AC8DEDF233BF", "I have to go back home. Ask other Digimon if you have questions.")
